




Queries to Back up: 
WQL query for Device Collection based on AD Device Group: select SMS_R_SYSTEM.ResourceID,SMS_R_SYSTEM.ResourceType,SMS_R_SYSTEM.Name,SMS_R_SYSTEM.SMSUniqueIdentifier,SMS_R_SYSTEM.ResourceDomainORWorkgroup,SMS_R_SYSTEM.Client from SMS_R_System where SMS_R_System.SystemGroupName = "INFONET\\SOFT-Adobe Acrobat PRO (USA)-CPU"
WQL query for User Collection based on AD User Group: select SMS_R_USER.ResourceID,SMS_R_USER.ResourceType,SMS_R_USER.Name,SMS_R_USER.UniqueUserName,SMS_R_USER.WindowsNTDomain from SMS_R_User where SMS_R_User.UserGroupName = "INFONET\\SOFT-Print Server Change Script- Solon-USER"
WQL Query for Installed Application - Prompt for Application Name: select distinct SMS_R_System.Name, SMS_R_System.LastLogonUserName, SMS_R_System.OperatingSystemNameandVersion, SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.SystemType, SMS_R_System.IPSubnets, SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.DisplayName, SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.Version, SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.InstallDate, SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.ProdID, SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.Publisher, SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.Model from  SMS_R_System inner join SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM on SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId inner join SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS on SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId where SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.DisplayName like ##PRM:SMS_G_System_ADD_REMOVE_PROGRAMS.DisplayName##
WQL Query for Installed Software - Prompt for Product Name : select distinct SMS_R_System.Name, SMS_R_System.LastLogonUserName, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.SoftwareCode, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ARPDisplayName, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ProductVersion, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.InstallDate, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.InstallSource, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.Publisher, SMS_R_System.OperatingSystemNameandVersion, SMS_R_System.Build, SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.SystemType, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.InstalledLocation, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.InstalledLocation, SMS_G_System_X86_PC_MEMORY.TotalPhysicalMemory, SMS_R_System.IPSubnets from  SMS_R_System inner join SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE on SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId inner join SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM on SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId inner join SMS_G_System_X86_PC_MEMORY on SMS_G_System_X86_PC_MEMORY.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId where SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ARPDisplayName like ##PRM:SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ARPDisplayName## 
WQL Query for Installed Software by Publisher - Prompted : select distinct SMS_R_System.Name, SMS_R_System.LastLogonUserName, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ARPDisplayName, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ProductVersion, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.InstallDate, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.InstallSource, SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.Publisher, SMS_R_System.OperatingSystemNameandVersion, SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.SystemType, SMS_R_System.IPSubnets, SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.Model from  SMS_R_System inner join SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE on SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId inner join SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM on SMS_G_System_COMPUTER_SYSTEM.ResourceID = SMS_R_System.ResourceId where SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.Publisher like ##PRM:SMS_G_System_INSTALLED_SOFTWARE.Publisher## 
